identity: Cybele's existence is not known to the general public of Earth.
knownrelatives: Zuras (husband, deceased), Thena (formerly Azura, daughter), Mentor (formerly Alars, brother-in-law), Starfox (Eros, nephew), Thanos (nephew, deceased)
powers: Cybele possessed superhuman strength, durability, and stamina. She could also manipulate energy and psionic powers of the mind such as hypnosis.
